nodes.text: A human female served as a TIE Fighter Pilot in the naval forces of the First Order. She flew under the callsign "Epsilon Six" thirty years after the Battle of Endor as a member of Epsilon Squadron, a Starfighter Squadron comprised of TIE/fo space superiority fighters. Epsilon Six took part in the battle on Takodana during the First Order's conflict with the Resistance.
